> rejection is another kind of throttle, what's your idea of throttle?

@jerryshao 
I was thinking we could delay the session creation, because, at least for our workloads, there are short bursts in requests to Livy. Delaying the session creation just by 1 or 2 minutes solves those problems.

@jerryshao 

> Travis is not so stable, you need to trigger several times to make it pass.

